how to stay happy charged and energised all through the day hi pratishtha good to see someone seeking the emotional high road it is a worthy quest and it can be done i have some experience in this area and here are some things that have worked for me know that the atmosphere of your emotions is yours to command you don't have to be blown about by the winds of circumstance it is possible to establish a mental stance that is positive and not based in any way upon material circumstances you can simply choose to be happy it is that simple if it helps you can find some things about life that help establish that attitude but you don't have to happiness is a choice be aware that the vast majority of humans do not understand this and will be perplexed about your buoyant attitude you will be called a bliss ninny and be told that you are unrealistic our culture has come to think of misery and frustration as a natural part of life it is simply not true having said that be prepared to go through some days where you have to lower your levels of expression to accommodate those around you who are truly suffering people who are suffering a deep loss take no comfort from being around those who are happy and jubilant also folks will want to know how you do it i just tell them that happiness is a choice and that you cannot attach it to your outer circumstances that is it but you must practice it like learning music or anything else the vibrations around you will tend to drag you down may i suggest that you stop watching television i have observed that most of the programming these days tends to be negative and fearful just my two cents peace be with you will Happiness A Course In Miracles Meaning of life Transactional analysis Yoga Sutras of Patanjali Alcoholics Anonymous Comparing and contrasting Judaism and Christianity Sexual orientation Human Traumatic incident reduction Social psychology Psychoanalysis Religion Soul Sant Thakar Singh Philosophy of language Evil Current teachings 